Enkiroroto e Bildad


1  Neitoki Bildad le Shuhit awal, ejo:


2  Kenkata nabaa iyie ing'oru irorei?

Tujurru, ina peyie kiro.


3  Ainyoo peyie eikenari iyiook anaa nkishu?

Ainyoo peyie kira iyiook lmoda te dukuya iyie?


4  Iyie ilo opolos kewan te ngoro ino,

keing'uari enkop te nkaraki iyie,

arashu eiwuang'ieki endapidapoi aaitung'uaa ewueji enye?


5   Ee, ore ewang'an oo ltorrok netaaraki.

Ore olang'at le nkima enye nemeitoki awang.


6  Ore ewang'an naa kemisimis to lng'obor lenye,

ore oltaa otii shumata enye neari.


7  Ore iroruat enyena naagol neitodorropi,

ore inkoitoi enyena nenang'aa ninye.


8  Amu etanang'akaki atua orreshet too nkejek enyena,

nelo te nkoitoi nebatatakino.


9  Eibung orreshet entutunyo enye,

neirrag orreshet oibung ninye.


10  Eisudoro olgosoi lenye tiatua enkop,

orreshet otii enkoitoi enye.


11  Emanita ninye inaaitureisho te pooki alole,

nemir ninye too nkejek enyena.


12  Ore engolon enye apa, netaa taata olameyu te ninye,

netinyikaka ninye engolikinoto pee error.


13  Ore te nkaraki emuoyian netumute osesen lenye

ore olkikau le keeya netumuta irubat o sesen lenye.


14  Etopolosaki ninye teilo lng'obor apa oisilig

neyauni ninye aayaki ilo aiguanani oitureisho.


15  Netii olng'obor lenye ina neme enenye;

ebore enkima aidapashakino emanyisho enye pooki.


16  Etoito intona enyena tiabori

netoyu imbenek enyena too lukuny.


17  Neish endamunoto enye te nkop,

nemeeta enkarna too nkoitoi naalala.


18  Eturrumoyioki ninye te wang'an aanang'aki enaimin,

nerewi aaitung'uaa enkop.


19  Meeta ninye eishoi arashu iishoritin tiatua olorere,

nemeetae oloishu teine apa nemanya.


20  Ore lelo oomanya oloontoluo,

neing'asiate teina olong enye,

neibung ninche olkirutoto lo loosaen.


21  Esipa imanyishoritin kuna e lelo lemeure Enkai,

ewueji ene eilo lemeyiolo Enkai.

